                "name": "Primal Aura",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "Whenever Vildeis would be affected by a bleed effect, all enemies within 30 feet gain that bleeding condition instead, as though they were the effect\u2019s original targets (no saving throw, creatures immune to bleeding are immune to this effect). The Heal DC to stop this bleeding is 25."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Smite Evil",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "Vildeis can smite evil as a 20th-level paladin. Whenever she uses smite evil and successfully strikes an evil outsider, the outsider is also subject to <i>disintegrate</i>, using Vildeis\u2019s paladin level as the caster level. After the <i>disintegrate</i> effect and the damage from the attack are resolved, the smite effect immediately ends."
            },
